high_descs: Move forward to the stove on the left.
Pick up the tomato on the front of the counter.
Turn around, bring the tomato to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge.
Bring the chilled tomato back to the sink on the left.
Put the chilled tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the sink.

high_descs: walk straight to the counter by the stove
grab the tomato on the counter
turn around, turn around to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the tomato in, wait a while, take the tomato out
turn left, walk to the sink
put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: cool the tomato in the refrigerator, put the tomato in the sink

high_descs: Walk straight to the end of the counter. Turn around and go to the counter. Turn slight right to face the stove from the side.
Pick u the tomato next to the stove.
Turn around and take a step. Go to the right then turn right again to face the fridge.
Place the tomato on the shelf with the apple and shut the door. After a few seconds open the fridge and take out the tomato.
Turn to the left a few steps and turn left then a right to face the counter beside the sink.
Place the tomato on the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move the tomato from the fridge into the sink.
